“Building Value through  Equity Investing”
Focus. Research. Judgment.
Mark Asset Management, founded in 1985, is an SEC-registered investment adviser based in New York City seeking to maximize returns over time, through an established stock selection process and the active management of Long-Bias and Long-Only hedge fund strategies. Morris Mark, founder of Mark Asset Management and an award winning industry veteran, has years of experience in the financial markets and has professionally managed capital for over 30 years. He leads a team of 16 experienced investment and operations professionals.



