This is a brand page for the EVERGREEN trademark by Evergreen Asset Management Corp. 
                                in Purchase, , 10577.
Write a review about a product or service associated with this EVERGREEN trademark.    
                                Or, contact the owner Evergreen Asset Management Corp. of the EVERGREEN trademark by filing a request to communicate with    
                                the Legal Correspondent for licensing, use, and/or questions related to the EVERGREEN trademark.
                           






On Thursday, August 10, 1995,  a U.S. federal trademark registration was filed for 
                        EVERGREEN by 
                        Evergreen Asset Management Corp., Purchase 10577.
                        The USPTO has given the EVERGREEN 
                        trademark serial  number of  74714062.  
                        The current federal status of this trademark filing is ABANDONED - FAILURE TO RESPOND OR LATE RESPONSE.
                        The correspondent listed for EVERGREEN is 
                        
                        
                                            DALBERT U. SHEFTE of 
                                            KENNEDY COVINGTON  LOBDELL & ET AL,  BANK OF AMERICA CORPORATE CENTER, SUITE 4200 100 NORTH TRYON STREET CHARLOTTE, NORTH CAROLINA
                                .
                            The EVERGREEN trademark is filed in the category of 
                            
                                    Insurance & Financial Services
                                . 
                            The description provided to the USPTO for EVERGREEN 
                            is advisory administrative and management services for mutual fund investments. 
                            





