Mark Asset Management Corporation: Private Company Information - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 26, 2017 1:17 AM ET
Capital Markets

Company Overview of Mark Asset Management Corporation



Snapshot People




Company Overview
Mark Asset Management Corporation is an employee owned hedge fund sponsor. The firm primarily provides its services to High net worth individuals. It also caters to pooled investment vehicles, pension and profit sharing plans, charitable organizations, trusts, and offices. The firm manages separate client-focused equity portfolios. It firm launches and manages hedge funds. The firm invests in the public equity markets. It employs long-bias and long–only strategy to make its investments. The firm primarily invests in growth and value stocks. The firm employs fundamental analysis to create its portfolios. Mark Asset Management Corporation was founded in 1985 and is based in New York City.


667 Madison Avenue9th FloorNew York, NY 10065United StatesFounded in 1985



Phone: 212-372-2500

Fax: 212-372-2525

www.markasset.com







